14 Kusalattika, Chagocchakaduka
Kusalattika, Chagocchakaduka
30.
73Akusalaṃ saññojanaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  ganthaṃ…pe…  oghaṃ…pe…  yogaṃ…pe…  nīvaraṇaṃ…pe…  parāmāsaṃ. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
74Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe tīṇi…pe…  avigate pañca. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
